_text = "Out of some unknown instinct, I reach my hand out.\n\nA bird flies out from the treeline and lands on my fingers.\n\nWe look at each other for a moment. Its as if the bird sees me and understands what Im going through. It can see the jealousy in my eyes, wishing I could fly freely as it.\n\nIt takes a moment to rest, then flies back into the treeline. Disappearing out of site.\n\nIm left alone once again, wondering if maybe I should have followed it.\n\nMy memory of this place ends here."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MemoryTunnelRoom3, MemoryTunnelRoom3, false)
